Anybody got any ideas there?

00:06:20.010 --> 00:06:21.740
Early experiences.

00:06:21.740 --> 00:06:22.780
SUSAN WOJCICKI: I'll start.

00:06:22.780 --> 00:06:25.340
I'm not sure, really, like,
any one thing prepared me.

00:06:25.340 --> 00:06:25.920
I was lucky.

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:28.270
I joined Google when it was
a really small company.

00:06:28.270 --> 00:06:30.330
