like that, you see a lot of

00:10:43.150 --> 00:10:46.080
benefits on that, not only for
what your company's going to

00:10:46.080 --> 00:10:48.890
achieve, but also what you'll
get to be part of within that.

00:10:48.890 --> 00:10:50.030
So I think that's good advice.

