00:19:24.900 --> 00:19:28.810
get it done by this time really
motivated people and it

00:19:28.810 --> 00:19:32.070
made us more efficient at
really getting that out.

00:19:32.070 --> 00:19:32.970
MEGAN SMITH: Which is good.

00:19:32.970 --> 00:19:37.060
And also having the habit of
setting stretch goals, as part

00:19:37.060 --> 00:19:39.500
of the goals, and then letting
your team not achieve 100%,

00:19:39.500 --> 00:19:42.060
but try to get to 80% and then
set more stretch goals.

00:19:42.060 --> 00:19:45.120
